{"tid":593322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣港人命案 台灣僅通緝兇嫌！殺人追討期僅30 年 恐永遠結不了案","createTime":"2018-03-15T01:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T02:56:51.000Z","uid":22349,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b0660c6027022ce5904fdaa4191a52df3e359be4","tid":593322,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T01:31:58.000Z","msg":"香港一對情侶來台遊玩，港女遭男友殺害棄屍，因兇嫌已逃回香港，法界人士認為，台港無引渡協議，最糟情況是「永遠結不了案」。<br />\n<br />\n《自由時報》報導，陳同佳行兇後回香港，依我國司法管轄規定，香港屬人、台灣屬地，雙方均有管轄權。士林地檢署表示，士檢已分案調查，但港台沒有司法互助或引渡協議，港警若不送兇嫌來台受審，全案最後會以通緝方式處理，目前殺人追訴期為30年，若修法取消殺人致死追訴期後，該案結局可能是「永遠無法結案」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"59173a7fafb67bbb8b2696bcceeb17a918356d63","tid":593322,"uid":81995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T01:42:41.000Z","msg":"以後會唔會有人參考哩單 case 黎殺人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56960b24f85c64d757d2fa12267735cd2b9486c8","tid":593322,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59173a7fafb67bbb8b2696bcceeb17a918356d63","tid":593322,"uid":81995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T01:42:41.000Z","msg":"以後會唔會有人參考哩單 case 黎殺人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T01:43:51.000Z","msg":"都要叫到條友陪你去台灣先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都唔係無方法嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d330fac8a8942521baf96af739c75598aa4f83","tid":593322,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T01:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3162/3162243.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3162%2F3162243.jpg&h=c38b7c0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41a72c4d0327b5854490969b150ba00cc635cebc","tid":593322,"uid